{
  "stem": "15396.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know, I felt not one second that I was doing something against my country.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On the contrary, in fact, I think that if we had opened the door much quicker, much, much quicker-- In fact, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Roosevelt, who started this organization, was one of the prime movers in getting things started that way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Emergency Rescue Committee.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was quite impressed with, I think, Konrad Heiden and a few other people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she tried to get someone-- Varian Fry, who, as I was saying, is the most idealistic man I've ever met, he had been in Berlin and he had seen all this.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he told everybody in America.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a-- a professor with a bow tie and silk handkerchief.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Never read a spy novel in his life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she couldn't get anybody else to take this job, to go over and-- and try and rescue these people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, well, all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you can't, I'll try, but I mean, I wouldn't know how to go about it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he found out how to go about it, and he did it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From America by Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Roosevelt.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Really, by-- by the Emergency Rescue Committee, but she was the-- the force that--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--behind it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think Mr Roosevelt winked his eye to it a little bit, because we were always upset that the government didn't help more.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I even sent a very facetious telegram one time, long time later, which I probably better not tell, because it was so off.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I was noted for doing a few rather radical things at time, and, but I don't think it helped my standing in the-- in the State Department very much.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
